text: Eugenia capensis, the dune myrtle, is a species of plant in the family Myrtaceae, which is native to East and southern Africa. ==Subspecies== The subspecies are: * E. capensis subsp. albanensis (Sond.) F.White * E. capensis subsp. capensis * E. capensis subsp. gueinzii (Sond.) F.White * E. capensis subsp. natalitia (Sond.) F.White * E. capensis subsp. nyassensis (Engl.) F.White * E. capensis subsp. simii (Dummer) F.White * E. capensis subsp. zeyheri (Harv.) F.White ==References== ==Further reading== * Hilton-Taylor, C. et al. 1998.
